      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah that \"street-smart\" vs \"unrefined\" angle is huge for comedy. people love riffing on that. can you give me some specific joke premises or little \"bits\" based on that? like, maybe something about how people judge them in certain settings, or how they act compared to others when they're trying to be \"proper\"? just give me some actual comedic setups I can use.",
